  m_text: "Congratulations!\r\n\r\nYou\u2019ve successfully repaired and improved
    clean energy systems!\r\n\r\nBy working with solar panels, wind turbines, and
    eco-friendly lighting, you\u2019ve helped reduce pollution and support a more
    sustainable future.\r\n\r\nWhy it matters:\r\nClean and affordable energy (SDG
    7) helps protect our planet, reduces climate change, and ensures everyone has
    access to reliable power.\r\n\r\nEvery small action counts \u2014 and you\u2019ve
    made a big difference!\r\n\r\nThank you for helping build a cleaner, greener
    world "
